1226 2399 MT
(Federal, State, local laws, ordinances and regulations relating to safety and health renders this Purchase Order invalid)SH
1226 2424 MT
(unless Seller obtains NBC's written waiver of either the conflicting specifications or Seller's obligation to deliver an item)SH
1226 2449 MT
(which conforms to the requirements of such laws, ordinances or regulations.)SH
1226 2499 MT
(22. EQUAL EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITY - Seller, where required by law, hereby agrees to comply with Executive)SH
1226 2524 MT
(Order 11246, as amended, in its implementing regulations, including the Equal Opportunity Clause set forth in Section 202)SH
1226 2549 MT
(of the order and 60-1.4 \(A\) of the regulations of the Secretary of Labor, Title 42 CFR, Chapter 60, Parts 1-60, which are)SH
1226 2574 MT
(incorporated in this Purchase Order by reference.In addition, this Purchase Order incorporates by reference the)SH
1226 2599 MT
(Affirmative Action Clauses of the Rehabilitation Act of 1973, at 41 CFR 60-741.4, and the Vietnam ERA Veterans)SH
1226 2624 MT
(Readjustment Act of 1974, at CFR 60-250.4.)SH
1226 2674 MT
(23. NBC REFERENCE - Any reference in this Purchase Order to NBC shall be deemed to include any NBC subsidiaries)SH
1226 2699 MT
(or affiliated companies, as applicable.)SH
