(1. PRICES / TAXES / QUANTITIES - Prices shown on the face of this Purchase Order  shall be firm and fixed unless)SH
44 351 MT
(otherwise agreed to in writing by an authorized representative of NBC. Unless otherwise provided herein, such prices)SH
44 376 MT
(include all applicable federal, state and local taxes.  Shipments shall not vary from quantities specified herein unless)SH
44 401 MT
(agreed to in writing by NBC.)SH
44 451 MT
(2. ACCEPTANCE / INSPECTION / REJECTION - By acceptance of this Purchase Order and/or performance hereunder,)SH
44 476 MT
(Seller agrees to comply fully with the terms and conditions of sale set forth on both the front and reverse sides of this)SH
44 501 MT
(document, and any supplements hereto which are incorporated by a reference herein.  Acceptance of this Purchase Order)SH
44 526 MT
(is expressly limited to the terms and conditions contained herein and none of Seller's terms and conditions in)SH
44 551 MT
(acknowledging or accepting this Purchase Order shall apply.   Acceptance of the goods or services under this Purchase)SH
44 576 MT
(Order shall not constitute acceptance of Seller's terms and conditions.  No employee, representative or agent of NBC has)SH
44 601 MT
(any authority to bind NBC unless specifically included within this Purchase Order or as a written amendment hereto and)SH
44 626 MT
(signed by an authorized representative of NBC's Sourcing Department.  Seller may not ship under reservation.  Final)SH
44 651 MT
(inspection and acceptance of goods and services shall be on NBC's premises unless otherwise agreed to in writing.)SH
44 676 MT
(Nonconforming goods shall be returned freight collect, and Seller shall be debited for the inbound transportation cost plus)SH
44 701 MT
(handling expense.  If any of  the goods ordered are found at any time to be defective in material or workmanship, or)SH
44 726 MT
(otherwise not in conformity with the requirements of this Purchase Order or specifications set forth to Seller by NBC, in)SH
44 751 MT
(addition to such other rights, remedies and choices as it may have by contract or by law, NBC at its option and sole)SH
44 776 MT
(discretion may: \(a\) reject and return such goods at Seller's expense; \(b\) require Seller to inspect the goods and remove)SH
44 801 MT
(and replace nonconforming goods with goods that conform to the Purchase Order or specifications set forth by NBC or \(c\))SH
44 826 MT
(require Seller to repair nonconforming goods at a facility designated by NBC.   If NBC elects option \(b\) above and Seller)SH
44 851 MT
(fails to promptly make the necessary inspection,)SH
44 876 MT
(removal and replacement, NBC may at its option inspect and sort the goods and return all nonconforming goods to Seller;)SH
44 901 MT
(Seller shall pay thecost thereof.)SH
44 951 MT
(3. DELIVERIES / REMEDIES / WAIVER - \(a\) Time is of the essence for this Purchase Order.  If Seller fails to make)SH
44 976 MT
(deliveries or perform the services at the time agreed upon, or performs the work hereunder in such a fashion as to)SH
44 1001 MT
(endanger its aability to make timely deliveries or render timely performance of services, NBC reserves the right to cancel,)SH
44 1026 MT
(purchase elsewhere, and hold Seller accountable for any additional cost and damages incurred by NBC.   Goods)SH
44 1051 MT
(purchased F.O.B. Seller's plant or shipping point shall not be considered delivered until they reach the NBC receiving point)SH
44 1076 MT
(as set forth herein or such other shipping point as may be agreed to in writing; however NBC assumes responsibility at the)SH
44 1101 MT
(F.O.B. point for transportation charges \(where applicable\), provided such goods are either adequately prepared and)SH
44 1126 MT
(packed \(or prepared and packed in accordance with the packaging specifications set forth by NBC where applicable\) for)SH
44 1150 MT
(shipment by Seller. \(b\) If it is determined that it is necessary to correct actual or anticipated failures or hazards in its)SH
44 1175 MT
(products attributed to a defect or nonconformity in goods provided by Seller under this Purchase Order, Seller shall)SH
44 1200 MT
(reimburse NBC for any and all actual expenses which NBC incurs as a direct or indirect result of such failure or hazard. \(c\))SH
44 1225 MT
(Rights and remedies of NBC hereunder are cumulative and in addition to those which NBC has under law and equity. \(d\))SH
44 1250 MT
(Any waiver by NBC of any particular breach or default hereunder by Seller shall not constitute a continuing waiver or a)SH
44 1275 MT
(waiver of any other breach or default. \(e\) Approval by NBC of Seller's proposed design, test plans and/or procedures,)SH
44 1300 MT
(manufacturing process, methods, tooling or facilities shall not relieve Seller from meeting all requirements of this Purchase)SH
44 1325 MT
(Order.)SH
44 1375 MT
(4. WARRANTY - Unless a different warranty is agreed upon and set forth herein, Seller warrants all goods and/or services)SH
44 1400 MT
(delivered or provided hereunder to be free and clear of all liens, encumbrances, security interests or other claims, free)SH
44 1425 MT
(from defect in design, materials or workmanship, fit for the purpose intended for a period of twelve \(12\) months from)SH
44 1450 MT
(delivery to, and acceptance by NBC, to conform strictly to the specifications, drawings or sample specified or furnished)SH
44 1475 MT
(and any supplementary documentation referenced herein. In the event that any of the goods or products are software,)SH
44 1500 MT
(Seller represents and warrants that, where applicable, each such goods or services does not contain  any code,)SH
44 1525 MT
(programming instruction, or set of instructions that is intentionally  constructed to damage, interfere with or otherwise)SH
44 1550 MT
(adversely affect operation of those goods or other computer programming code, data files, or hardware without the)SH
44 1575 MT
(consent and intent of the product user. Seller further warrants that it has not received and knows of no claim made or)SH
44 1600 MT
(proceeding brought by a third party on the basis that any goods or services infringes or utilizes a patent, copyright, trade)SH
44 1625 MT
(secret or trademark of a third party and that no patent, copyright, trade secret or trademark of a third party has been used)SH
44 1650 MT
(without permission to manufacture or complete such product or has been incorporated therein without permission. Seller)SH
44 1675 MT
(further warrants that it complies with the requirements of all applicable federal, state and local laws, rules, ordinances and)SH
44 1700 MT
(regulations such as, but not limited to OSHA, Hazardous Materials Transportation Act, Toxic Substances Control Act and)SH
44 1725 MT
(Consumer Product Safety Act.  This warranty shall survive any inspection, delivery or acceptance of the goods or services,)SH
44 1750 MT
(or payment therefore by NBC.)SH
44 1800 MT
(5. CHANGES - \(a\) NBC may at any time, by a written order, and without notice to the sureties, make changes within the)SH
44 1825 MT
(general scope of this Purchase Order in any one or more of the following: \(i\) drawings, designs or specifications; \(ii\))SH
44 1850 MT
(method of shipment or packing; and \(iii\) place of delivery. If any such change causes an increase or decrease in the cost)SH
44 1875 MT
(of the item required for the performance of any part of the work under this Purchase Order, whether changed or not)SH
44 1900 MT
(chnaged by any such Purchase Order, an equitable adjustment shall be made in the price or delivery schedule, or both,)SH
44 1925 MT
(and the Purchase Order shall be modified in writing accordingly, subject to Seller obtaining NBC's prior written approval of)SH
44 1950 MT
(such modified price or delivery schedule. Any claim by Seller for adjustment under this clause shall not excuse Seller from)SH
44 1975 MT
(proceeding with this Purchase Order as changed. \(b\) NBC Engineering, Technical and other personnel may from time to)SH
44 2000 MT
(time render assistance or give technical advice to or exchange information with Seller's personnel concerning this)SH
44 2025 MT
(Purchase Order or the articles or services to be furnished hereunder. However, this shall not constitute a waiver with)SH
44 2050 MT
(respect to any of Seller's obligations or NBC's rights hereunder or be authority for any change in the goods or services)SH
44 2075 MT
(called for hereunder. Any waiver or change to be valid and binding upon NBC must be in writing and signed by an)SH
44 2100 MT
(authorized representative of NBC's Sourcing Department. In case of any doubt, Seller should promptly consult NBC's)SH
44 2125 MT
(Sourcing Department for further instructions. \(c\) In connection with any claim for adjustment under this clause, Seller shall)SH
44 2150 MT
(submit cost data in such form and detail as may reasonably be required by NBC; if this Purchase Order related to a prime)SH
44 2174 MT
(contract with the U.S. Government, Seller shall, upon NBC's request, submit a Certificate of Current Cost or Pricing Data,)SH
44 2199 MT
(in substantially the form set forth in section 3-8074 of the Armed)SH
44 2224 MT
(Services Procurement Regulation, with respect to such data. \(d\) Where the cost of property is made obsolete or)SH
44 2249 MT
(is excessive as a result of a change included in Seller's claim for adjustment pursuant to this clause, NBC shall)SH
44 2274 MT
(have the right to prescribe the manner of disposition of such property.)SH
44 2324 MT
(6. BANKRUPTCY - In the event of any proceedings, voluntary or involuntary, in bankruptcy or insolvency by or against)SH
44 2349 MT
(Seller, including any reorganization or arrangement proceeding, or in the event of the appointment, with or without Seller's)SH
44 2374 MT
(consent, of an assignee for the benefit of creditors or a receiver, then NBC may cancel this Purchase Order for default and)SH
44 2399 MT
(hold Seller accountable for any additional costs or damages incurred by NBC.  NBC's only liability shall be payment in)SH
44 2424 MT
(accordance with this Purchase Order for deliveries previously made or for goods covered by this Purchase Order, then)SH
44 2449 MT
(completed and subsequently delivered in accordance with the terms of this Purchase Order.)SH
44 2499 MT
(7. THIRD PARTY CONTRACT / ASSIGNMENT - Neither this Purchase Order nor any rights and obligations under it shall)SH
44 2524 MT
(be assigned or contracted to a third party by Seller without the prior written consent of NBC, except that claims for monies)SH
44 2549 MT
(due or to become due under this Purchase Order may be assigned by Seller without such consent, and subject to the)SH
44 2574 MT
(provisions of this paragraph.  NBC shall promptly be furnished with written notice and a signed copy of any such)SH
44 2599 MT
(assignment.  Payment to an assignee of any such claim shall be subject to set-off or recoupment for any present or future)SH
44 2624 MT
(claim or claims, which NBC may have against Seller, except to the extent that any such claims may be expressly waived in)SH
44 2649 MT
(writing by NBC.  Seller shall ensure that subject to the foregoing, any third party contract and/or assignment made)SH
44 2674 MT
(hereunder shall incorporate the provisions of this Purchase Order by specific reference hereto.)SH
44 2724 MT
(8. NBC PROPERTY - All materials, tools, plates, artwork, film, drawings, specifications and similar items furnished or paid)SH
44 2749 MT
(for by NBC shall be: clearly identified as NBC property, removable by NBC at any time at no additional cost, used only in)SH
44 2774 MT
(filling NBC Purchase Orders, inventoried by Seller, kept separate from other such materials, treated confidentially and not)SH
44 2799 MT
(disclosed to any third party, and disposed of by Seller as NBC shall direct.  Seller shall be responsible for loss or damage)SH
44 2824 MT
(to any such NBC property, excepting normal wear and tear, and shall furnish NBC a written inventory upon request. )SH
